igns with plausible Amharic word formation for negation ('አል-') and noun derivation ('-ነት') from the verb 'ወሰነ' (to decide). The root is 'ወሰነ'.","input_words":["የአለመለየት","የአለምመሪዎች","የአለቆችንም","የአለታወንዶ","የአሊማዞን","የአሊባባን","የአሊዩ","የአሊያ","የአላሙዲ","የአላድዝ","የአሌክስንድሮስና","የአልሆል","የአልም","የአልቃድሪፍ","የአልኖድ","የአልውስነትነት","የአልጀብራዊ","የአልጃዚራ","የአሎኤስ","የአሐርሔልን","የአሐስባይ","የአሐዳዊነት","የአሔር","የአሕላብንም","የአሕላይ","የአሕመድ","የአሕዛብንስ","የአሕዛይ","የአመራሮቻችን","የአመስጋኞቹ"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"63eb8c98-8cb3-4d52-9456-f4ed9c72703d","created_at":"2026-03-02T13:57:07.902383+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_25/chunk_0367.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Adjective","root":"አስቸኳይ","word":"የአሰቸኳይ","synonyms":["urgent","emergency","critical","pressing"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"አሰናጅ","word":"የአሰናጆቹ","synonyms":["the preparers","the organizers","the arrangers"],"importance":6},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማስገደድ","word":"የአሰገደች","synonyms":["she made him bow","she made him prostrate","she compelled him to bow"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Noun","root":"አሳም","word":"የአሳም","synonyms":["pig","swine","hog"],"importance":6},{"pos":"Noun","root":"አሳሪ","word":"የአሳሪው","synonyms":["the binder","the captor","the imprisoner","the one who ties"],"importance":6},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማሳል","word":"የአሳሳለ","synonyms":["he made him sharpen","he made him hone"],"importance":4},{"pos":"Noun","root":"አሳብ","word":"የአሳባቸውን","synonyms":["their thoughts","their ideas","their opinions"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"አሳነባሪ","word":"የአሳነባሪ","synonyms":["one who makes read","reciter","reader (causative)"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Noun","root":"አሳንሰር","word":"የአሳንሰሩ","synonyms":["the elevator","the lift"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"አሳንሰር","word":"የአሳንሰሩን","synonyms":["the elevator (accusative)","the lift (accusative)"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"አሳዳጊ","word":"የአሳዳገዎች","synonyms":["guardians","foster parents","rearers"],"importance":6},{"p